<!--
  ==================================================
  Quest Rewards Patch — Challenge Turn-In XP Grants
  @version     1.0.0
  @date        2025-08-14
  @author      Demonata Gaming

  @group       QuestRewardAdjustments
  @applies_to  Config/quests.xml
  @description
    Restores experience payouts for challenge chains by explicitly
    setting Exp rewards on the final trader turn-in quests. Under
    Demonata Core’s XP rework these chains don’t award XP unless
    specified here, so this keeps progression sane.
  @notes
    - Fires on completiontype=TurnIn at the trader.
    - Only edits reward[@type='Exp']/@value for listed quest IDs.
    - Keep aligned with progression.xml level/attribute curve.
  ==================================================
-->
